    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111550/extras/bc6d7a4536ab16431d2afdbd31271fe2.avif?t=1771911125\" width=1560 height=165 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >量子神力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在一次失手的行窃中，世上最顶尖（也最名副其实）的“猫盗”——<strong>灵爪米腾斯</strong>意外陷入一场量子实验，并由此获得了<strong>不可思议的力量</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111550/extras/37e04ae2ca9fd9e592aff56a5308f883.poster.avif?t=1771911125\" width=1170 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111550/extras/37e04ae2ca9fd9e592aff56a5308f883.webm?t=1771911125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在朋友们的协助和一系列新习得的量子技能加持下，米腾斯必须在这个诡秘的研究设施中解开层层谜题<strong>揭露背后真相</strong>，并赶在早餐前成功回家。   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111550/extras/237c708c053e0a545a7ea77f92520c27.avif?t=1771911125\" width=1560 height=165 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >趣味拼图</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 游戏围绕一项核心<strong>量子机制</strong>展开——按下按键，米腾斯便能一分为二，两只猫均可独立操控，既能协作解谜，也能各享其乐。    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111550/extras/3d38d08091667884d26f1927d116b599.poster.avif?t=1771911125\" width=1170 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111550/extras/3d38d08091667884d26f1927d116b599.webm?t=1771911125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >但其中暗藏玄机</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >量子叠加态遵循<strong>海森堡不确定性原理</strong>——当无人注视时，米腾斯可能身处任何位置。可一旦暴露在视野之内（被观测），一切便坠入理论……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚪穿过那扇理应开启的门，避开虚幻（理论上并不存在）的监控。.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧵 量子猫咪， <i>不可阻挡！</i>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111550/extras/caff2e8cbbacea9d7abd3cd7f443e9ce.avif?t=1771911125\" width=1560 height=165 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可爱的猫咪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 暂时抛开<i>理论物理</i> 来体验时尚。解锁众多<i>古怪又迷人</i>的自定义内容，每款装扮都可用于任一量子形态 ——闪耀猫步秀场吧。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111550/extras/85f739098679ba38542d04d46e88f4b2.poster.avif?t=1771911125\" width=1170 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111550/extras/85f739098679ba38542d04d46e88f4b2.webm?t=1771911125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 以异能，行无路之路，避必至之劫，取不可取之物。终成<strong>灵猫大盗！</strong>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111550/extras/8cd3fb1e84d073aed46561736e5ec6f2.avif?t=1771911125\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一场<i>独一无二</i>的量子冒险！ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心特色：</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🧬 烧脑谜题挑战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一系列分身解谜关卡，跨越<strong>理论时空</strong> 传送物品及能量，还能及时赶回家吃早餐！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎨 全方位自定义系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >畅玩装扮搭配，自由选择定制帽子、猫咪品种、个性配饰，<strong>连小猫的丰满度都由你决定。</strong>. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👥 好友一同玩乐</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持好友随时<strong>加入/退出的本地合作模式</strong>, 亦可通过 Steam 远程同乐功能与好友一同闯关。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🤫揭开实验室奥秘</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这所隐秘机构究竟在研究什么？除害机器人到底在守护何物？而那只神秘的<strong><i>影喵</i></strong>又是谁…?<i> </i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏆 丰富扩展内容</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏区域、狡诈的机械鼠、刁钻的量子碎片——层层关卡献给追求挑战的解谜爱好者。当然，如果你只是想当只小猫<strong>摔摔杯子</strong>, 那也不是不行… </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎮 绝密作弊指令</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>上、下、顶、底、奇、魅</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持来自： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111550/extras/f38c6a129ab5b37d290c8efc5267d046.avif?t=1771911125\" width=540 height=150 /></span></p>",
